==English==
===Noun===

[[Image:Bang icon 32x32.jpg|!]] The symbol '''!''' is a called an ''exclamation mark'' or ''[[exclamation point]]''.  
#[[Punctuation]] used to denote excitement, surprise or shock: ''The dam has burst, run for your lives!''
#In some [[computer language]]s, it is called a '''[[shreek]]'''.  
#When used in [[e-mail]] to represent a separator for an e-mail address, it is called a '''[[bang]]'''.

